{
  "texts": [
    "The overall risk of bias score was determined for each study based on the number of criteria for high risk of bias met.",
    "Studies are considered to have a low risk of bias if no domains are rated as high risk and most domains are rated as low risk.",
    "Studies with some concerns in one or more domains but no high-risk ratings are considered to have some concerns.",
    "If any domain is rated as high risk, the study is considered to have a high risk of bias.",
    "Software and toolsData were managed and analyzed using R version 4.2.1."
  ]
}